## Josh's Driver Assistant

#### Josh is the inventor of an AI-powered device that allows drivers to control their car climate, media, and more using just their voice.  

#### After an initial round of testing, Josh noticed that drivers with higher pitched voices, the majority of whom were women, had a significantly harder time getting the device to accurately understand their voice prompts.


#### Now Josh needs to make a decision about what to do with this new information

